longBusinessSummary: DeFi Technologies Inc. engages in the building and management of assets in the decentralized finance sector in Canada. It focuses on the enhancement of shareholder value through various investments, including the acquisition of DeFi protocols, equity, debt, or other securities of publicly traded or private companies, or other entities. The company was formerly known as Routemaster Capital Inc. and changed its name to DeFi Technologies Inc. in February 2021. DeFi Technologies Inc. is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
